name: Invesco Canadian Government Floating Rate Index ETF
longDescription: PFL seeks to replicate to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses the performance of the FTSE Canada 13 Year Laddered Floating Rate Note Index or any successor thereto. This Invesco ETF invests primarily in Canadian government and corporate investment grade floating rate notes. PFL seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the FTSE Canada 1 3 Year Laddered Floating Rate Note Index, or any successor thereto. This Invesco ETF invests primarily in Canadian government and corporate investment grade floating rate notes.
